observationText: The NCC-MPNST2-C1 cell line had a doubling time of 57 hours.
The NCC-MPNST2-C1 cell line exhibited considerably strong invasive potential in in vitro invasion assays.
The NCC-MPNST2-C1 cell line had higher invasion ability compared to four other NCC-MPNST cell lines in a real-time cell analysis (RTCA) invasion assay.
The NCC-MPNST2-C1 cell line harbored the potential to form spheroids, which are used as in vitro 3D tissue micro-analogs in cancer research.
